		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:16,000",
				"to": "00:01:18,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 76000,
				"to": 78000
			},
			"text": " So why would that happen?"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:18,000",
				"to": "00:01:22,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 78000,
				"to": 82000
			},
			"text": " The answer comes down to what people are actually using AI for."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:22,000",
				"to": "00:01:27,350"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 82000,
				"to": 87350
			},
			"text": " A couple of years ago, most AI usage was scattered, writing, research, general"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:27,350",
				"to": "00:01:29,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 87350,
				"to": 89000
			},
			"text": " question answering."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:29,000",
				"to": "00:01:33,880"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 89000,
				"to": 93880
			},
			"text": " Today, coding has taken over as the single largest use case, making up more"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:33,880",
				"to": "00:01:37,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 93880,
				"to": 97000
			},
			"text": " than half of all activity on major AI platforms."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:37,000",
				"to": "00:01:39,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 97000,
				"to": 99000
			},
			"text": " And here's the thing about coding tasks."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:39,000",
				"to": "00:01:43,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 99000,
				"to": 103000
			},
			"text": " Most of them aren't asking the model to solve some brilliant novel problem."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:43,000",
				"to": "00:01:47,970"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 103000,
				"to": 107970
			},
			"text": " They're asking it to auto-complete a function, refactor a file, write a test,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:47,970",
				"to": "00:01:49,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 107970,
				"to": 109000
			},
			"text": " fix a small bug."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:49,000",
				"to": "00:01:53,260"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 109000,
				"to": 113260
			},
			"text": " That kind of work doesn't need a model operating at the very edge of reasoning"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:53,260",
				"to": "00:01:54,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 113260,
				"to": 114000
			},
			"text": " ability."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:54,000",
				"to": "00:01:58,630"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 114000,
				"to": 118630
			},
			"text": " It needs a model that's fast, cheap, and good enough, running at massive volume"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:58,630",
				"to": "00:02:00,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 118630,
				"to": 120000
			},
			"text": " all day, every day."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:00,000",
				"to": "00:02:03,050"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 120000,
				"to": 123050
			},
			"text": " And that's exactly the lane where models like Xiaomi's have optimized hard,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:03,050",
				"to": "00:02:06,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 123050,
				"to": 126000
			},
			"text": " strong at coding specifically,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:06,000",
				"to": "00:02:09,430"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 126000,
				"to": 129430
			},
			"text": " price digressively, and available at a scale that makes them the default choice"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:09,430",
				"to": "00:02:14,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 129430,
				"to": 134000
			},
			"text": " for exactly the kind of repetitive, high volume work that dominates real usage."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:14,000",
				"to": "00:02:18,160"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 134000,
				"to": 138160
			},
			"text": " Meanwhile, the models that top the intelligence charts, the ones built and"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:18,160",
				"to": "00:02:22,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 138160,
				"to": 142000
			},
			"text": " priced for the hardest reasoning tasks, end up used differently."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:22,000",
				"to": "00:02:26,550"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 142000,
				"to": 146550
			},
			"text": " They still get called on, but for a narrower slice of work, complex debugging,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:26,550",
				"to": "00:02:30,420"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 146550,
				"to": 150420
			},
			"text": " high stakes analysis, the kind of task we're getting at wrong actually costs"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:30,420",
				"to": "00:02:31,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 150420,
				"to": 151000
			},
			"text": " something."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:31,000",
				"to": "00:02:34,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 151000,
				"to": 154000
			},
			"text": " High intelligence, lower volume."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:34,000",
				"to": "00:02:37,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 154000,
				"to": 157000
			},
			"text": " It's not that these models are being rejected."
